
Bloodfist Help:  Construct Bloodward

Guild level:  8
Honor Req:    0
Base Cost:    80

  Construct a bloodward out of 3 corpses which will heal all Bloodfist
guild members in the room for an amount of time based on the life energy
of the corpses.  A bloodward can not be moved after it has been created,
and will fall apart when the life energy of the corpses has been drained.
A bloodward can not be constructed from sacrificed corpses.

Usage:  construct bloodward

